1
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,040
Mr. Gu, Mr. Gu!

2
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,180
I was wrong.

3
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,360
I was blind to not recognize you.

4
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,440
Please be the bigger person

5
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,280
and let me off.

6
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,280
I will never do it again.

7
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:10,180
I have to put on a full show.

8
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,890
I need to teach him a lesson.

9
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:17,770
Grandpa,

10
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,680
let's go.

11
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,120
Mr... Mr. Gu.

12
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,340
I was wrong, Mr. Gu.

13
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,610
I was wrong. I was wrong.

14
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,280
Please spare the Lei family.

15
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,640
Mr. Gu, you're here.

16
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,500
Please come in.

17
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,210
Where is Ziqing?

18
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,720
The young lady is still changing clothes.

19
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,979
Here, this way please.

20
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,370
Have a seat here.

21
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,560
Please wait a moment.

22
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:01,440
This is my first time at Ziqing's house.

23
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,080
I hope I can use this opportunity

24
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,140
to find some clues.

25
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,000
Zixi,

26
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,850
today is your birthday too.

27
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,680
If only you

28
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,370
were still here.

29
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:56,820
This is for you.

30
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,940
It looks just like you.

31
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:01,770
Perfect.

32
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,160
When I'm not around,

33
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:03,760
hugging it

34
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,440
is like hugging me.

35
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,600
Recently,

36
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:41,320
during the development of the TG new energy racing project,

37
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,579
an accident occurred.

38
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,560
Lead designer Song Haoming resigned to take responsibility,

39
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,079
and the project was shelved again.

40
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:49,079
I just feel like this whole thing...

41
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,079
Gu Haoran.

42
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,200
Ziqing.

43
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,440
Why are you touching my sister's things?

44
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,500
I got lost just now.

45
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,960
I thought this was your room.

46
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,560
I'm sorry.

47
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,080
My sister passed away.

48
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,620
Everything in this room belonged to her.

49
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,580
Please don't touch anything.

50
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,160
Your sister passed away five years ago.

51
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:19,959
I know.

52
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,370
She was a very good girl.

53
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,120
Don't pretend you knew her well.

54
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,040
You didn't even know her.

55
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,490
I heard you mention her.

56
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,040
It seems you two were close.

57
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,120
My sister and I were the closest.

58
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:46,960
Back then,

59
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,720
when I insisted on learning to race,

60
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,560
only my sister encouraged me

61
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,560
and supported me.

62
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,240
The biggest regret of my life

63
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,740
is that when she had her accident,

64
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,840
I was still abroad

65
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,820
and couldn't come back to be with her.

66
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,120
I'm sorry.

67
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,680
Ziqing.

68
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,240
I specifically went to the temple

69
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,840
to get this bracelet for you.

70
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,580
I know you love racing,

71
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,540
so I truly support your dream.

72
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,680
Although

73
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,240
your sister might

74
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,640
never have the chance to see you race in person again,

75
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,640
she definitely hopes more than anyone

76
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,880
that you stay safe.

77
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,159
Let this bracelet take our place

78
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,440
to accompany you on every journey

79
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,240
and every lap.

80
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:59,200
No matter where you are, you must remember.

81
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,760
In a corner of this world,

82
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,840
someone is always silently caring for you,

83
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,700
waiting for you

84
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,140
to return home safely.

85
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:44,920
Ziqing.

86
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,980
Why did you kiss me?

87
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,640
This is my gift in return.

88
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,720
Starting today,

89
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,860
you are my personal property.

90
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:01,920
Got it?

91
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,900
I am your brother-in-law.

92
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,320
So,

93
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,060
you can't flirt with other girls either.

94
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,360
I didn't.

95
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,500
You say you didn't?

96
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,320
Then what is this?

97
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,200
This?

98
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,760
The media is just trying to get attention.

99
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,880
They are just chasing shadows.

100
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,480
There is nothing between us.

101
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,640
That's more like it.

102
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:35,200
Our families are going to be allied by marriage.

103
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,260
You must draw a line with other girls,

104
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,130
understand?

105
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,680
Sounds like

106
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:41,770
you're jealous.

107
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:46,480
No.

108
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,620
It's a matter of pride.

109
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,720
Our families will be allied by marriage in the future.

110
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,000
If you create scandals like this,

111
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,560
where does that leave the Chen family's pride?

112
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:55,920
Okay.

113
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,620
As you command.

114
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,330
That's more like it.

115
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:06,880
Trash.

116
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:10,200
You can't even handle such a small task.

117
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,210
Lord Qianye.

118
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,490
Please give me one last chance.

119
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,420
Do you think I'll still trust you?

120
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,740
As for this matter,

121
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,880
stay out of it.

122
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:27,290
I'll arrange for someone else to investigate the truth.

123
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,799
You must be tired after walking around all day.

124
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,059
Go home and rest early.

125
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,440
Okay.

126
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,320
You should go back early too.

127
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:48,960
Haoran.

128
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,640
What's wrong?

129
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,440
You celebrated my birthday with me today.

130
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,300
I'm very happy.

131
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,280
Really?

132
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,720
It seems my efforts weren't in vain.

133
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,200
Okay.

134
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,840
Then hurry up and go back.

135
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:03,680
Bye.

136
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,480
Bye.

137
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,480
Captain,

138
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,080
you finally contacted me.

139
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,160
You've been missing for five years.

140
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:53,960
Where have you been?

141
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,960
Where are you now?

142
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,320
I'll tell you slowly later.

143
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,880
There's an urgent matter now.

144
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,600
I found some clues about Zixi.

145
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:03,160
I need your help to restore them.

146
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,520
Okay.

147
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,890
Then send them to me.

148
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,480
Okay.

149
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:06,960
Then I'll deliver them to you later.

150
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,520
Then I'll wait for you at home.

151
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:08,960
Bye.

152
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:21,920
Young master.
